item.title: COVID-19 Data Exploration
item.description: Help prevent the spread of COVID-19 The COVID-19 disease caused by the SARS-CoV-2 virus is a global humanitarian challenge. Please help flatten the curve by doing the five. Follow your local public health guidelines at the CDC. Stay informed at Google’s information hub. Situation in the United States As an attempt to understand the trends of the virus so far, I have aggregated some public available data and visualized their general trends.
